*Trči* po hladnom večernjem vazduhu. (Run in the cold evening air.)

Kad dete vidi leptira, ono *trči* za njim. (When a child sees a butterfly, it runs after it.)

U dvorištu se *trči* za loptom. (In the yard they are running after the ball.)

Ona *trči* maraton. (She is running a marathon.)

*Trčali* smo svi skupa na stadion. (We all ran to the stadium together.)

*Trčeći* svojim putem, uspeo sam da stignem na vreme. (Running my way, I managed to get there on time.)

Oni *trče* uzbrdo. (They are running uphill.)